  "prompt": "Which are the good CA coaching centres in south Delhi?",
  "response": "There are several reputable coaching centers for Chartered Accountancy (CA) in South Delhi. Here are a few well-known options:\n\n1. **First Attempt** - Known for its structured courses and experienced faculty.\n2. **Envision** - Offers comprehensive CA programs with a focus on practical knowledge.\n3. **CA Shubham Bansal Classes** - Popular for personalized attention and good results.\n4. **The CA Institute** - Provides courses for all levels of CA with experienced instructors.\n5. **Vsmart Academy** - Focuses on conceptual clarity and exam strategies.\n\nWhen selecting a coaching center, consider factors like faculty qualifications, student reviews, batch size, and proximity to your location. It's also a good idea to visit the centers or attend trial classes if available to find the best fit for your learning style.",
